             was indicted for <rs id="t18020602-29-off160" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020602-29-off160" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020602-29-off160" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020602-29-cd161" type="crimeDate">15th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020602-29-off160 t18020602-29-cd161"></join>, twenty yards of linen cloth, value 20s. a piece of nankeen, value 5s. two yards of calico, value 2s. and a calico wrapper, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18020602-29-victim248" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Clarke
                  <interp inst="t18020602-29-victim248" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
